{
  "id": "6a511a073be7cb0872f4fc45",
  "title": "2026/07/11",
  "created": 1783699976,
  "updated": 1783881911,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a511a073be7cb0872f4fc45",
      "text": "2026/07/11",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699976,
      "updated": 1783699976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a076eb4060000003f09a7",
      "text": "第28週: 日月火水木金[[土]]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699976,
      "updated": 1783699976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a076eb40600000007c149",
      "text": "2026年 52.60％経過",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699976,
      "updated": 1783699976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a076eb406000000a93ef8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699976,
      "updated": 1783699976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a140000000000ff06be",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699989,
      "updated": 1783699989
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a140000000000ff06bf",
      "text": "\t[inajob-with-ai]を人のデータと比較している",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699989,
      "updated": 1783700001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a220000000000ff06c1",
      "text": "\t\t面白い",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700003,
      "updated": 1783700004
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a8f0000000000ff06c6",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://github.com/nishio/external_brain_in_markdown GitHub - nishio/external_brain_in_markdown · GitHub]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700112,
      "updated": 1783700115
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a920000000000ff06c7",
      "text": "   \tnishioさんをみつけたので、比較相手に使わせてもらっている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700115,
      "updated": 1783700129
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511aa00000000000ff06c8",
      "text": "   \t\tライセンスが書いてないので、この比較データの公開はしないほうがよさそう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700129,
      "updated": 1783700143
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51b7b000000000002412ab",
      "text": "   \t\tCC-BYでいいよ[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1783740336,
      "updated": 1783740345
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bb80000000000081e57d",
      "text": "   \t\tわーい[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783741313,
      "updated": 1783741317
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51e16100000000005500d0",
      "text": "   \t文字としては同じだが指している対象が違うような事例を探してきてその違いを説明するみたいなコンテンツができてきた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783751010,
      "updated": 1783751040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51e18000000000005500d1",
      "text": "   \t 指している対象が同じで認識が違うものを見つけてほしいがgraspでは厳しそう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783751041,
      "updated": 1783751066
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51e19a00000000005500d2",
      "text": "   \t これはこれで自分のまとめた概念を深掘りするきっかけにはなる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783751067,
      "updated": 1783751087
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51e1d000000000005500d3",
      "text": "   \t 1ページをじっくり読んで、AIの解釈違いとかを自分の日記に書き戻すとよさそうだが、今は時間がない問題があるなぁ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783751120,
      "updated": 1783751166
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51e1fe00000000005500d4",
      "text": "   \t  スマートフォンでポチポチできるようにしたい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783751166,
      "updated": 1783751174
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51ef310000000000d05989",
      "text": "   \t https://inajob-ai-nishio.pages.dev/",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783754546,
      "updated": 1783754548
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51ef330000000000d0598a",
      "text": "      まだ作りかけですが、公開してみる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783754548,
      "updated": 1783754557
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51ef600000000000d0598b",
      "text": "      [Hypothesis]でコメントできるようにしてる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783754593,
      "updated": 1783754627
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51ef820000000000d0598c",
      "text": "       主に自分用",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783754627,
      "updated": 1783754631
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51ef900000000000d0598d",
      "text": "       ページがリネームされたり内容が改定されたときどうなるかは不明",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783754641,
      "updated": 1783754671
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5216950000000000943964",
      "text": "       静的ページにコメント機能を実装できて便利だった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783764630,
      "updated": 1783764643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a310000000000ff06c2",
      "text": "\t\t[grasp]のおかげで、コンテキストに乗らないような巨大な情報源から情報を取り出せている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700018,
      "updated": 1783700040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a4a0000000000ff06c3",
      "text": "\t\t\t多分[RAG]的なものでも似たような体験が得られるだろう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700043,
      "updated": 1783700056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a580000000000ff06c4",
      "text": "\t\t\tドキュメントがWikiやCosense的な構造なら[grasp]が楽",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700057,
      "updated": 1783700086
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511ada0000000000ff06c9",
      "text": "\t\tinajob-with-aiのページを読み、そこから抽出したキーワードをnishioから検索・分析し、pages/にページを作成する一連の処理",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700187,
      "updated": 1783700219
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511ada0000000000ff06ca",
      "text": "  \tStep 1: inajob-with-aiのページを適当にいくつか読む",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700187,
      "updated": 1783700230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511ae60000000000ff06cc",
      "text": "  \tStep 2: 抽出したキーワードをnishioから検索",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700199,
      "updated": 1783700199
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511aeb0000000000ff06cd",
      "text": "  \tStep 3: 比較分析の整理",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700204,
      "updated": 1783700204
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511af30000000000ff06ce",
      "text": "  \tStep 4: pages/にページを作成",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700212,
      "updated": 1783700212
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a076eb40600000062fd37",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699976,
      "updated": 1783699976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a514176000000000024fb56",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783710071,
      "updated": 1783710073
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51417a000000000024fb57",
      "text": " ワールドカップのスペイン ベルギー戦見に起きる",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783710075,
      "updated": 1783710088
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5196570000000000685efa",
      "text": " 青学にきた",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783731799,
      "updated": 1783731803
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5228d4000000000085ac97",
      "text": " 赤坂見附駅にて。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783769300,
      "updated": 1783769305
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5228d8000000000085ac98",
      "text": " \t新宿に行きたい。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783769305,
      "updated": 1783769309
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5228dd000000000085ac99",
      "text": " \tぼーっとしてて「池袋方面」の電車に乗ってしまう。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783769309,
      "updated": 1783769320
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5228f1000000000085ac9a",
      "text": " \t東京のなんとなく西側で思ってての間違い。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783769329,
      "updated": 1783769350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a515a790000000000240e20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783716529,
      "updated": 1783716529
    },
    {
      "id": "6a515a7a0000000000240e22",
      "text": "[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783716530,
      "updated": 1783716530
    },
    {
      "id": "6a515a7b0000000000240e23",
      "text": " 今日も完璧な朝",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783716531,
      "updated": 1783716536
    },
    {
      "id": "6a515a790000000000240e21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1783716529,
      "updated": 1783716529
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5172ec0000000000602920",
      "text": "[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1783722732,
      "updated": 1783722732
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5172ed0000000000602921",
      "text": " [2026/07/05#6a4a3828000000000082fb48]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1783722733,
      "updated": 1783722735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5172f10000000000602923",
      "text": "  先に電源を変えたもののだめで、原因はマザボだった",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1783722737,
      "updated": 1783722758
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5172f70000000000602924",
      "text": "  のでエイヤと思ってCPUもクーラーも、電源もメモリも変えた",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1783722743,
      "updated": 1783722778
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51731b0000000000602925",
      "text": "  GPUとケースは以前変えてたので、もう残ってるパーツがWindows入ってたSSDしか無い",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1783722779,
      "updated": 1783722825
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51733c0000000000602926",
      "text": "  これが[テセウスの船]…",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783722812,
      "updated": 1783729183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51750d0000000000450b86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1783723278,
      "updated": 1783723278
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51750e0000000000450b87",
      "text": "[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1783723278,
      "updated": 1783723280
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5175110000000000450b89",
      "text": "　グループチャットでやりとりすると、トピックごとに会話出来なくてやめてーと思うんだけど、チャネル分けて、スレッド立てて、ちゃんと件名つけて投稿するって面倒なんだろうなあ",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1783723281,
      "updated": 1783723466
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5175f10000000000450b8a",
      "text": "　　[パーソナルアシスタント]がうまくやってくれるのを待つか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1783723505,
      "updated": 1783805187
    },
    {
      "id": "6a517e39000000000038fe28",
      "text": "　　Cosenseのように、途中で脱線しても後から事後的に別のスレッドとして分岐させられる仕組みがあってほしい[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783725625,
      "updated": 1783725795
    },
    {
      "id": "6a536293000000000056117e",
      "text": "　　　[再利用の目的が決まってから適切な切り出しが決まる]これに近い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783849621,
      "updated": 1783849644
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51750e0000000000450b88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1783723278,
      "updated": 1783723278
    },
    {
      "id": "6a517caa0000000000f11a83",
      "text": "[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783725227,
      "updated": 1783725228
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5226180000000000084c4b",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/4c78dc4c60ccacf4cc07784f6b4cf478]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768601,
      "updated": 1783768739
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5226a20000000000084c4c",
      "text": "サムネ権を行使",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768739,
      "updated": 1783768750
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d7940000000000c52a8c",
      "text": " 当直開け！眠れた",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783748501,
      "updated": 1783748509
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d79d0000000000c52a8d",
      "text": " 眠れたけど7時に病棟から血ガス取ってくれという依頼で起こされて不服そうにしている",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783748509,
      "updated": 1783748547
    },
    {
      "id": "6a518a5900000000009d6586",
      "text": "\t例の三つ子",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783728730,
      "updated": 1783728730
    },
    {
      "id": "6a518a5100000000009d6584",
      "text": "\thttps://x.com/A_shimatarou/status/2075412190602178813?s=20",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783728722,
      "updated": 1783728724
    },
    {
      "id": "6a518e3c0000000000df882d",
      "text": "\t　か、かわいい[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783729725,
      "updated": 1783729729
    },
    {
      "id": "6a517cac0000000000f11a85",
      "text": " ちょっと歩くと想像以上に汗かく",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783725228,
      "updated": 1783736983
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51ac0b000000000095aa02",
      "text": " 　[[水分補給をすすめてくるふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1783737355,
      "updated": 1783737398
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d0d300000000002157ce",
      "text": " ロイホ行った",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783746771,
      "updated": 1783746777
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225940000000000084c46",
      "text": "  ハンバーグにフライドポテトが付いてしまうため揚げ物避けて肉がっつりという選択肢が限られている",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768469,
      "updated": 1783768504
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225c00000000000084c47",
      "text": "  サイゼ行けばよかった。うまかったけど",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768513,
      "updated": 1783768521
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d7790000000000c52a8b",
      "text": " ちょっと遠出して[白桃シュガーバターカスタードクレープ]←インスタで見てめっちゃ気になってしまった を食べた、残念ながら桃が味せず",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783748473,
      "updated": 1783812260
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225500000000000084c42",
      "text": "  真面目に作ってはいるぽく食感が良かった、[クレープ]と[ザラメ]をもっちゃもっちゃザリザリしていたらみずみずしいものが入ってくる的な",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783768401,
      "updated": 1783812286
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225680000000000084c43",
      "text": "  お店がとんでもなく繁盛していた",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768425,
      "updated": 1783768430
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225d30000000000084c48",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/03c77bdac1fa4c409c567a2428b0c74f]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768531,
      "updated": 1783768579
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5226020000000000084c4a",
      "text": "  隠れる桃",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768579,
      "updated": 1783768587
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51fbe500000000000fe3b8",
      "text": " うんこの色良くなるといいね！",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783757798,
      "updated": 1783757804
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5227e40000000000084c4f",
      "text": " [金津園]で一番かかるくらいの人に相手してもらった、普通に楽しかった",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783769061,
      "updated": 1783779763
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225370000000000084c40",
      "text": " やりたいこと",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768376,
      "updated": 1783768379
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225340000000000084c3f",
      "text": "  はま寿司に行く",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768372,
      "updated": 1783768451
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5225870000000000084c44",
      "text": "  やりたいことを整理する",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783768456,
      "updated": 1783768459
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52355600000000001ad6f6",
      "text": " 桃 本日二度目",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783772503,
      "updated": 1783772509
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52355d00000000001ad6f7",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/79134d9389308a52ad20942b8647d0df]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783772509,
      "updated": 1783772518
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52356800000000001ad6f9",
      "text": " [パニール]あえ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783772521,
      "updated": 1783772526
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52445500000000003ff55f",
      "text": " クレープ2",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783776341,
      "updated": 1783776348
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52445d00000000003ff561",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/a39df1f62a4797175f7c186be429356d]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783776349,
      "updated": 1783776359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a532c4a000000000039bf11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783835723,
      "updated": 1783835723
    },
    {
      "id": "6a532c4a000000000039bf12",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/65e3ae6e9b659c0cf86cbfed546dea07]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783835723,
      "updated": 1783835735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a532c5a000000000039bf13",
      "text": "サモサを頼んだら絶品の[トマトチャトニ]が付属してきて神であった",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783835738,
      "updated": 1783835756
    },
    {
      "id": "6a532db80000000000699362",
      "text": " いいなすぎる[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783836088,
      "updated": 1783836093
    },
    {
      "id": "6a532dbd0000000000699363",
      "text": "  よく行く店のトマトチャトニ日によって味が違いすぎて好みの日とそうじゃない日がありすぎる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783836093,
      "updated": 1783836125
    },
    {
      "id": "6a532dee0000000000699364",
      "text": "   しょうが強めの日とライム強めの日が好み",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783836142,
      "updated": 1783836162
    },
    {
      "id": "6a534ce90000000000f20650",
      "text": "   (何を入れて作ってるのか考えたこともなかった[はるひ.icon])",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783844074,
      "updated": 1783844089
    },
    {
      "id": "6a517e8a000000000066d7f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783725705,
      "updated": 1783725705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a517e8a000000000066d7f3",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783725705,
      "updated": 1783725713
    },
    {
      "id": "6a517e8d000000000066d7f4",
      "text": " [おは.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783725713,
      "updated": 1783725718
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5197ce0000000000bb5121",
      "text": " 情報の集まり方を妄想",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732173,
      "updated": 1783732523
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5197d50000000000bb5122",
      "text": "  方向性を持って集める時",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732180,
      "updated": 1783732415
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5198020000000000bb5124",
      "text": "   取りに行く",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732225,
      "updated": 1783732230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5198350000000000bb5128",
      "text": "   予測できる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732276,
      "updated": 1783732280
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5198140000000000bb5126",
      "text": "   例:xxxについて調べる時",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732243,
      "updated": 1783732517
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5197df0000000000bb5123",
      "text": "  雑多な情報の中から、特定の方向性が見えてくる時",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732190,
      "updated": 1783732417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51980a0000000000bb5125",
      "text": "   勝手に集まった、ように感じる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732233,
      "updated": 1783732475
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51983b0000000000bb5129",
      "text": "   予測しにくい",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732282,
      "updated": 1783732290
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51981e0000000000bb5127",
      "text": "   例:日記の束をllmに処理させてみる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732253,
      "updated": 1783732508
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5198590000000000bb512a",
      "text": "   例:ある時ふと、類似性に気付く",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732312,
      "updated": 1783732340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5198800000000000bb512b",
      "text": "  ふと気付く→方向性を持って集める→ふと気付く→と、ループもしていそう",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732351,
      "updated": 1783732385
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5199ea00000000004f31ba",
      "text": " 情報を集める→[熟成]期間→ふと気付く→のループがしっくり来た。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732713,
      "updated": 1783737761
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519a0900000000004f31bb",
      "text": "  寝かせる期間、脳みそに染み込む期間、自分の中のモデルに組み込む時間、が「ふと気付く」に繋がってる気がしてきた。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732744,
      "updated": 1783732920
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519afc00000000004f31bd",
      "text": "   時間が必要",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732987,
      "updated": 1783732992
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519baa00000000004f31be",
      "text": "   [腹落ちする]、的な。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783733161,
      "updated": 1783737752
    },
    {
      "id": "6a520da100000000006efc0b",
      "text": "   [デフォルトモードネットワーク]の話かな？ [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1783762337,
      "updated": 1783762364
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519a5800000000004f31bc",
      "text": "  最初はn個の方向性で集めてた独立した知識が、熟成されて共通項が見えてくる、的な。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783732823,
      "updated": 1783732895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519d030000000000f9e76b",
      "text": " ねむねむしぃので、帰って[昼寝]る",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783733506,
      "updated": 1783737740
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519d0f0000000000f9e76c",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1783733518,
      "updated": 1783733518
    },
    {
      "id": "6a517caa0000000000f11a84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783725227,
      "updated": 1783725227
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519abb00000000000aced5",
      "text": "[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783732924,
      "updated": 1783732925
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519abc00000000000aced7",
      "text": "　ページの切り出しにおける[\" from]は直接の祖先を示唆する",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783732925,
      "updated": 1783732942
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519acd00000000000aced9",
      "text": "　　それはそれとして別のページからも参照することができる。この、経緯の説明と広がりが同時にある感じがよい",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783732942,
      "updated": 1783732965
    },
    {
      "id": "6a522bb30000000000084c50",
      "text": "　　いいかも[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1783770039,
      "updated": 1783770040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a519abb00000000000aced6",
      "text": " 米が、食べたくなった。",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783732924,
      "updated": 1783756791
    },
    {
      "id": "6a523dcd00000000009be54c",
      "text": " 結構[気温がちょうど良すぎて最高]だった",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783774670,
      "updated": 1783774682
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51f7f20000000000a79fe0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783756787,
      "updated": 1783756787
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51afcc0000000000e040ef",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783738874,
      "updated": 1783738875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51afce0000000000e040f0",
      "text": " やること多すぎ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783738875,
      "updated": 1783738875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51afd30000000000e040f1",
      "text": " aiでいろんなことできるようになったせいで欲望に歯止めが効かなくなった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783738875,
      "updated": 1783738875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51b0040000000000e040f2",
      "text": "  今まで「とはいってもできない」だったのが「がんばればできる」になってしまった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783738875,
      "updated": 1783738875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a523e1400000000009be54d",
      "text": "  　[やれそうな自信があることをやめられない]状態になっている感じがある（自分の話）[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1783774741,
      "updated": 1783774761
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5250100000000000637cc3",
      "text": "  　 わかりすぎ[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783779345,
      "updated": 1783779348
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51b0290000000000e040f3",
      "text": "  仕方ないので生産性を上げるべくループ設計というやつをやっている",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783738875,
      "updated": 1783738875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51b04c0000000000e040f4",
      "text": "  とてもyak",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783738875,
      "updated": 1783738875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51b10e0000000000e040f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1783738875,
      "updated": 1783738875
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51b7c100000000002412ac",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1783740353,
      "updated": 1783740355
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51b7d900000000002412af",
      "text": "　[ジオゲッサー河川敷2026-07]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1783740378,
      "updated": 1783881911
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bc19000000000072d53b",
      "text": "[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783741466,
      "updated": 1783741472
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bc1f000000000072d53d",
      "text": " [Via Browser]とかいうのを試している",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783741472,
      "updated": 1783741481
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d26f000000000003e824",
      "text": "  とにかく軽いのでChromeすらストレージにアタックされるような端末で使ったことある[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1783747184,
      "updated": 1783747265
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bfd1000000000024bd01",
      "text": "  用途を絞ればいい感じかも[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783742418,
      "updated": 1783765009
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52181100000000001ac520",
      "text": "   検索結果ページにアクセスした時、自動的にキーワードを抽出してアドレス欄に入れておいてくれる機能がうれしい",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783765010,
      "updated": 1783765067
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52184a00000000001ac521",
      "text": "   [デライト専用ブラウザ]にしよっと",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783765067,
      "updated": 1783765100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a52186c00000000001ac522",
      "text": "    PWAには非対応っぽくて惜しい",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783765102,
      "updated": 1783765114
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5217cb00000000001ac51f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783764940,
      "updated": 1783764940
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bfd2000000000024bd02",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783742418,
      "updated": 1783742419
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bfd3000000000024bd03",
      "text": " 過去に調べ上げたFirefoxの拡張機能を全部書いていたら空しくなってきた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783742419,
      "updated": 1783742451
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bfed000000000024bd04",
      "text": " \tWebの閲覧には毎日たくさん時間を使っているとはいえ、こんなに時間をかけて調べ上げる意味はあったのか？と自問自答",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783742446,
      "updated": 1783747395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d2b70000000000442e58",
      "text": " [https://hoagecko.hatenablog.com/entry/general-addons-for-firefox Firefoxの拡張機能のおすすめ一覧 - PC・Androidのアドオンを紹介 - hoageckoのブログ]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783747262,
      "updated": 1783747263
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d2ba0000000000442e59",
      "text": " \t[https://hoagecko.hatenablog.com/entry/special-addons-for-firefox 特定のサイト・サービスに基づくFirefox拡張機能のおすすめ一覧 - hoageckoのブログ]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783747263,
      "updated": 1783747299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d2ce0000000000442e5a",
      "text": " \t投稿した",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783747278,
      "updated": 1783747282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d2df0000000000442e5b",
      "text": " 軽いブラウザといえば、[NetSurf]というブラウザが滅茶苦茶動作が軽かった記憶",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783747296,
      "updated": 1783747329
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d3010000000000442e5c",
      "text": " \t[Amiga]でも動くとか",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783747329,
      "updated": 1783747341
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d30c0000000000442e5d",
      "text": " \t最初期のCSSしか動かない骨とう品ブラウザ",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783747341,
      "updated": 1783747356
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51d34d0000000000442e5e",
      "text": " \t\tJSは無論不可",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783747406,
      "updated": 1783747412
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51bc19000000000072d53c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1783741466,
      "updated": 1783741466
    },
